<D>__{what's needed is cooperation...}
<A>__{hearing his own voice reverberate through the cavernous factory brings bertie's stutter back in full form.}
<C>__{bertie }
<D>__{...buh buh between the cuh cuh classses...}
<A>__{one of the workers sullenly pulls a chain, releasing a blast from a steam whistle that drowns bertie out.}
